name: Jellyfish (itch) (Wisik)
description:
You are a jellyfish that is trying to survivein the sea.

Angry Fish are attacking from all of the sides and on top of that, every 30 seconds your controls are being randomized! Slay the fish using your shock and try to get as high score as you can!

How everything works is explained in the game by clicking a button "How to play"
